title: Millimetre A/W  Hair Collection @ MUSE Soho for Little Princess Trust
desc: Come and join us on 24th November, 2015, for an evening of fun, frivolity, fabulous hair and fashion, all in aid of The Little Princess Trust - a charity dedicated to providing real hair wigs to children who have lost their hair to cancer. 7pm: Meet and Greet with complimentary bubbly and canapes. 8pm: Intro by Martha d'Arthur - drag queen extraordinaire...?https://twitter.com/MarthaDArthur 8.30pm: Catwalk show - prepare to be dazzled. 9pm: Speeches from Millimetre and The Little Princess Trust plus Music from Danny Charles. 10pm-late: Get your dancing shoes on! Music from DJ Cloud and special guest DJ. See you there :)
